snippet.title: Best VGM 2240 - Tales of Phantasia - Freeze
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1460 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XWd4539-gdk

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
Tales of Phantasia (1995)
Freeze
Motoi Sakuraba, Shinji Tamura & Ryota Furuya

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SupraDarky
